item.title: constants
item.description: PIXBUF_FEATURES_H GDK_PIXBUF_FEATURES_H PIXBUF_MAGIC_NUMBER Magic number for #GdkPixdata structures. GDK_PIXBUF_MAGIC_NUMBER PIXBUF_MAJOR Major version of gdk-pixbuf library, that is the "0" in "0.8.2" for example. GDK_PIXBUF_MAJOR PIXBUF_MICRO Micro version of gdk-pixbuf library, that is the "2" in "0.8.2" for example. GDK_PIXBUF_MICRO PIXBUF_MINOR Minor version of gdk-pixbuf library, that is the "8" in "0.8.2" for example. GDK_PIXBUF_MINOR PIXBUF_VERSION Contains the full version of the gdk-pixbuf header as a string. This is the version being compiled against; contrast with #gdk_pixbuf_version.
